WEBVTT

00:00:28.944 --> 00:00:34.639
If they found a paper
which had the wrong kind of thought,

00:00:34.663 --> 00:00:37.807
they could track down
who created that thought.

00:00:39.109 --> 00:00:40.703
And we in the West

00:00:41.894 --> 00:00:44.576
couldn't understand
how anybody would do this,

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:47.777
how much this would restrict
freedom of speech.

00:00:47.801 --> 00:00:51.077
We would never do that
in our own countries.

00:00:53.059 --> 00:00:59.476
But today, in 2011, if you go
and buy a color laser printer

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:03.339
from any major laser printer manufacturer